    "body": "Very strange indeed. I'm observing the same behavior. I changed the log statement to:\n\n``` js\nconsole.log(x, (new Date()).getSeconds())\n```\n\nAnd I see this:\n\n```\n888 31\n889 31\n890 31\n891 31\n892 31\n893 31\n894 31\n895 31\n896 41\n897 51\n898 52\n899 2\n900 12\n901 22\n902 32\n903 42\n```\n"
